name: The Rift, CONTAINMENT BREACH
description: Those who came before believed the precautions to be sufficient. They were not. Humans are driven by curiosity, they will always find a way into places that they shouldn't. In their quest for power, they opened doors that should have remained closed. Now we will all have to live with the consequences. Containment has been breached. Pray that what we have learned in this time of peace has been enough. The Dead God lives again.
